次自刀后即使赢了游戏，会在好友心中留下「为了赢不顾一切」的印象，人设在好友心中大打折扣，人设崩塌，再倒牌可能没人救你，游戏体验极差。 以上就是本人观点，欢迎反驳讨论，一起沟通交流。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-051eb2f85fcd90ae542756d6548f8473_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/365570825"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9ZThuo60+vZqEAMaCDQzNTE1OTEzIMia3vAFMCk44wlAGHIJMzY1NTcwODI1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1658151580.7973883", "card_id": "Q_543970761", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日本花滑选手羽生结弦将于 19 日召开记者会，或宣布自己是否会选择退役，你想说什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据日本广播协会（NHK）18 日报道，日本花样滑冰选手羽生结弦将于当地时间 19 日 18 时召开记者会，或宣布自己是否会选择退役。（央视）日本花滑选手羽生结弦将于 19 日召开记者会 或宣布去留"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-ef2c7382facb3092d0210019b6c4abd7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/543970761"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9ZThuo60+vZqEAMaCDgzMTY1MDEyINy41JYGMAc4aUAZcgk1NDM5NzA3NjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1658151580.7979827", "card_id": "Q_538653872", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 120}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高考后的暑假要学化妆吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f604d750af28413fffd3e6f450d8a5b0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/538653872"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9ZThuo60+vZqEAMaCDgxOTgzMDM1IK63wZUGMAE4hAFAGnIJNTM